A highly detailed, painterly illustration of a grotesque gorgon, Xatrid Butterface, with a dripping, viscous yellow substance around its mouth, a crazed expression, and multiple eyes. It stands amidst a shattered, opulent dining room, surrounded by overturned chairs and broken plates.  Deathtouch effect subtly implied through shimmering, ghostly outlines around the creature.  Style: Old master painting, dark fantasy, dripping gore, intricate detail, 8k.